{
  "id": "adv_event_2403_01_01",
  "title": "サニピ初の\n全国ツアー",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様～\n……雫ちゃん、何してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ everyone~.\n…What are you doing‚ Shizuku-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.674489593600001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ファンレター、読んでた……\n事務所に沢山届いてたから…",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been reading‚ fan letters…\nWe’ve received a lot at the office…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8666666667,
      "endTime": 10.7666665712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になってから\n一気にファンレターの数が増えたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we have become BIG4‚\nthe number of fan letters has increased dramatically.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.964398988,
      "endTime": 16.3666662852,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6002.267297199999
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8368.9339638
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "このファンレターは北海道……こっちは沖縄から……\nみんな、サニピのライブを生で観るのが夢だって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This fan letter is from Hokkaido… This one is from Okinawa…\nEveryone says their dream is to see a Sunny Peace live performance in real life…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5305665969,
      "endTime": 25.6542856215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "北海道に沖縄かぁ……もっといろんな場所でライブを\n開催出来ればいいんだけど、難しいよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hokkaido and Okinawa… It would be nice if we could hold live performances\nin more locations‚ but it’s difficult…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8520180384,
      "endTime": 35.2352604548,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9566.666666599996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなみんなに朗報があるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have good news for everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.418684705,
      "endTime": 38.3204546292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "さっき{user}君から聞いたんだけど……\nサニピ初の全国ツアーが決定したわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just heard from {user}-kun…\nSunny Peace’s first nationwide tour has been decided!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.518187046,
      "endTime": 45.053288268900005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "全国ツアー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A nationwide tour!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2510206858,
      "endTime": 47.422948066400004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "全国ツアーってことは\n日本中のファンの所に私達が会いに行けるんだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A nationwide tour means‚\nwe can go all over Japan to meet our fans!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5861901362,
      "endTime": 54.409681995700005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そういうこと！　それに関連して\n{user}君から宿題を預かってきたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! And in connection with that‚\n{user}-kun gave us some homework.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6195234696,
      "endTime": 61.387958280300005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "宿題って、なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Homework? What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.585690697,
      "endTime": 64.0268018325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "それはね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2245342493,
      "endTime": 65.72630264760001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.9740350644
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "第一回、全国ツアーのタイトルを考えよう会議～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The First \"Let’s Decide the Title of the Nationwide Tour\" Meeting~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0240350644,
      "endTime": 73.1591347615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.3568671782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "どんどんぱふぱふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bom Bom Honk Honk",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3568671782,
      "endTime": 75.2083638031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.4060962199
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、ライブツアーのテーマとなる\n『ツアータイトル』をみんなで考えましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ let’s all think of the theme of the live tour\nthat will be the “tour title” .",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4060962199,
      "endTime": 81.5078630923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.7389283338
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、アーティストのライブツアーには\n印象的なタイトルがつきものよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that artist live tours are usually\npaired with impressive titles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7389283338,
      "endTime": 88.0706742444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "ツアータイトルは、ポスターや告知で最初に目に付く\n大事な要素……これを決めるのは、責任重大……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The tour title is an important element that catches your eye first on posters\nand announcements… Deciding on this‚ is a big responsibility…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2722616671,
      "endTime": 96.4922617433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.6899941602
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ツアーのテーマになる魅力的なフレーズ……\nなんだか難しそうだね。どう考えたらいいのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An attractive phrase that will be the theme of the tour…\nIt sounds difficult. How should we approach this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.6899941602,
      "endTime": 106.9993363538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.1970687705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "ツアータイトルでよくあるのは、漢字一文字や\n四字熟語……『挑』とか『百戦錬磨』とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tour titles commonly use a single kanji character or a four-character idiom…\nLike “Challenge” or “Veteran of a Hundred Battles”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1970687705,
      "endTime": 117.117068656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "格好いい英単語もいいわよね\n『レボリューション』とか、そんな感じで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cool English words are good too.\nLike “Revolution” or something like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.3148010729,
      "endTime": 124.4404021738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.6481344062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "どれも悪くはないけど\nサニーピースらしさはあまり感じないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re not bad‚ but\nthey don’t really feel like Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.6481344062,
      "endTime": 130.6499104338,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.8476428507
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "短くて印象に残る、サニピらしいフレーズ……\nねぇ……『繋ぐ』なんてどうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A short and memorable phrase that’s like Sunny Peace…\nHey… How about “Connect”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8476428507,
      "endTime": 141.69226908669998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.7333329518
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.880976184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "繋ぐ……『SUNNY PEACE for\nYou and Me！』の歌詞にもあったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Connect… That was also in the lyrics of\n“SUNNY PEACE for You and Me!”.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.880976184,
      "endTime": 147.6827400046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.8804724215
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "「今までとこれからが繋がっていく」……\nこのライブツアーで過去と未来を繋ぐってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“The past and future are connected”…\nSo it means connecting the past and future through this live tour?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8804724215,
      "endTime": 156.2042141436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.4138057548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
